Package: shiny.ollama
Version: 0.1.0
Title: R shiny interface for chatting with LLMs offline on local with ollama
Description: Chat with LLMs on your machine without internet with complete privacy via ollama, powered by R shiny interface. For more information on ollama, visit <https://ollama.com>.
